</p><p class="- topic/p ">It can be used for the following ink cartridge RFID PBA's: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Ink system Cyan cartridge RFID</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 02PBA02 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">INK_3_CART_RFID</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Ink system Magenta cartridge lRFID</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 02PBA03 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">INK_4_CART_RFID</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Ink system Yellow cartridge RFID</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 02PBA04 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">INK_2_CART_RFID</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Ink system Black cartridge RFID</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 02PBA05 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">INK_5_CART_RFID</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Ink system White cartridge RFID</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 02PBA51 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">INK_6_CART_RFID</compsignal></comp> 
</p></li></ul></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Dis-assembly</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-F8EE43B1-36AF-4F86-8810-3B686A03AF19" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ul id="UL_21938DDBFE2C4558A2521E08DDCD31E9" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_53184B16D403439F881DA2AB90C20E0F" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper. 
</p></li><li id="LI_44FE05E8AA614EB29DDDC8E371A37315" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA012" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-1C874C66-3A17-4AC4-886B-753A1A37D196.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>02 Open the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_B134E67306214D50843B008D8457BAB1" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the lower cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA052" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-3EA4F7FC-3249-452F-A681-38FC94D794B9.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>24 How to remove the lower cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_1149587DF47D4799A15AB6BC627EEC69" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the middle cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA054" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-3DDBA7E4-FC98-4D59-B862-147D49213A2E.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>24 How to remove the middle cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_CA72C8A04562492B990FC422EBD62204" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the top cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA056" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0EC7B866-5C12-4DD8-B785-606D4BE4F19B.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>24 How to remove the top cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_3432EC3100EB49CA89DF91CE8E8459A6" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_586CF67276A04FDFB8E44CD278D897B6" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T10 
</p></li><li id="LI_E4F45EB0970745678042201DF4909330" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-56298206-EA31-4520-910F-170897DB8030" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-B632B297-FF5C-4950-9E80-B32F7784BCD6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C7A8FA39-4A5C-46D1-A41F-B79004690539-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C7A8FA39-4A5C-46D1-A41F-B79004690539-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_FC47EAC011BC4E2DA7A6FBD25F34DB71" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6CD2ADE1-7830-4D5F-8537-7B7AFE514E69-low.png" id="IMAGE_6EE79126D7BB4512B489C8DF594ABF6A" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6CD2ADE1-7830-4D5F-8537-7B7AFE514E69-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_C560ACCED69F4B4CB0C117A5318FED97" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table id="TABLE_B52E44417C814EDD91212EE7AEA3035A" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the ink bottle (cartridge). 
</p><note id="GUID-49235155-D3BE-4443-A613-CD2EA726B331" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">You can only remove an empty bottle. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_93D7F74A7C9A48C68A578CB95AADD1EE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E4548AC2-F2ED-464D-8728-E13F419DF111-low.png" id="IMAGE_6CE8E9DCF8AB4751A57EF3F8C7F1CCF5" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E4548AC2-F2ED-464D-8728-E13F419DF111-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 6 (T10) screws from the PBA. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-79BAE914-84CB-4FF7-8334-B1BD73399C86" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B60A2691-A9DC-4BCF-A988-4C77F19CC535-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B60A2691-A9DC-4BCF-A988-4C77F19CC535-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the connector and remove the PBA. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_F54D7A8982D045A1AEB7B0DE27E6FCFE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1C0277B2-67CF-4B97-892C-D9B53025C83D-low.png" id="IMAGE_E9C6BB2CA0FD42C0859EB96F0056EF23" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1C0277B2-67CF-4B97-892C-D9B53025C83D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_72D170EE68484FD7BED708497C742730" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7B546DCB-EEC9-4212-9F3E-8250B87A53D8-low.png" id="IMAGE_4EE5708BD18446D388196B4CFD616720" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7B546DCB-EEC9-4212-9F3E-8250B87A53D8-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_E3FC7EE10DDC46BA880F87671551C890" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-1CE85252-F6D3-4421-930B-8AE723FFB49C.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
